headline: Bernstein Reiterates Deere (DE) ‘Market Perform’ Rating on Brazil Growth Opportunities
summary: Deere & Company (NYSE:DE) is one of the 11 best industrial stocks to buy right now. On June 18, analysts at Bernstein reiterated a ‘Market Perform’ rating on the stock and a $548 price target. The bullish stance follows an analyst’s meeting with the company’s management in Brazil. headline: Can Deere Sustain Its 5-Year Double-Digit Dividend Growth Streak?
summary: DE's five-year dividend growth of 18.2% and consistent shareholder returns highlight its income strength, even as earnings decline.
